tcpdump -r tcpconnect_scan.pcap "tcp[13] = 0x02" | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d. -f1,2,3,4 | sort | uniq -c
	|````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
	+------	finds the host performing a scan in the pcap and how many connections were attempted
	
	
	
